From Theo Wawers Subject Re Sunrise sunset times There is a nice little tool in Lucid emacs It's called calendar On request it shows for given longitude latitude coordinates times for sunset and sunrise The code is written in lisp I don't know if you like the idea that an editor is the right program to calculate these things Theo W Theo Wawers LAHMEYER INTERNATIONAL GMBH email Lyonerstr phone D Frankfurt Main fax Germany